tika.dc.description: ENGLISH EDITION: This book will take us behind-the-scenes of her stardom and inside the music business. Jenni Rivera, a gentle woman often filled with doubt. A spiritual woman who lived in faith. A woman who gave of herself deeply to the community. A woman who wanted nothing more than to be loved, but who could only find it onstage. Told through Pete Salgado's and Gabriel Vazquez perspectives, both were Jenn's managers, and they share stories about the life of Dolores that no one knew and did not see on stage...
